origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
[['ResearchArticleSearch.find_articles', {'name': 'ResearchArticleSearch.find_articles', 'description': 'This function searches for research articles based on a topic and period.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'topic', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The topic of the research articles.'}, {'name': 'period', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The time period for the articles, e.g., last three months.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'articles', 'description': 'A list of up to five matching articles, each with a title, author, and publication date.'}]}], ['FinancialData.get_loan_default_rate', {'name': 'FinancialData.get_loan_default_rate', 'description': 'This function retrieves the loan default rate for a specific date and sector.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'date', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The date for which the data is requested.'}, {'name': 'sector', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The sector of finance, e.g., consumer finance.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'defaultRate', 'description': 'The loan default rate for the specified sector on the given date.'}]}], ['RiskAssessment.get_report', {'name': 'RiskAssessment.get_report', 'description': 'This function retrieves risk assessment reports for a specific sector.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'sector', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The sector of finance, e.g., consumer finance.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'report', 'description': 'A detailed risk assessment report for the specified sector.'}]}], ['CompanyStrategy.get_risk_management', {'name': 'CompanyStrategy.get_risk_management', 'description': 'This function retrieves risk management strategies for a specific company.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'companyName', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the company.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'strategy', 'description': 'The risk management strategy of the company.'}]}], ['RiskControl.get_suggestions', {'name': 'RiskControl.get_suggestions', 'description': 'This function retrieves risk control suggestions for a specific company.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'companyName', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the company.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'suggestions', 'description': 'Risk control suggestions for the company.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `ResearchArticleSearch.find_articles` 并传入 `topic` 和 `period`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "ResearchArticleSearch.find_articles",
    "args": "{'topic': 'consumer finance risk management', 'period': 'last three months'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
